author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-SK Hynix says does not expect major FX risk to Q4 earnings
text:
Oct 22 Sk Hynix Inc
* Says does not see major exchange-rate risk on Q4 earnings
* Says expects U.S. dollar-South Korean won exchange rate to revert to 1,150 to 1,160 levels
* Says 2016 capital expenditures may be slightly less than 2015 Further company coverage:
